    <h3  class="f4-mktg color-fg-muted pb-2" aria-hidden="true"> White Label: International Retailer</h3>
    <p  class="h6-mktg color-fg-default py-1 pb-sm-4 text-semibold" aria-hidden="true">The world’s third largest retailer partners with GitHub to drive innovation through open source best practices.</p>
